<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25750083">《西游记》中有哪些有趣的冷知识？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2482809" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
