<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="408">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ming-tian-de-ming-tian-de-ming-tian-26" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ming-tian-de-ming-tian-de-ming-tian-26" class="zg-link" title="明天的明天的明天">明天的明天的明天</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-peng-3-8" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-peng-3-8" class="zg-link" title="刘鹏">刘鹏</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2482809" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">常言道“吓屎了，吓出翔了”，西游里也有这么一出。<br><br>且看《西游记》第七十四回《长庚传报魔头狠　行者施为变化能 》。<br><br>猪八戒去找一个过路老头问附近妖怪的情况。<br>一开始老头说有三个妖怪，二师兄还很不屑，后来老头又说他们手下加起来有好几万的妖怪。<br><br>其中就包括这个著名的“小钻风”。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/a218d2340f0cc7ae848cb68aeae060ed_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="486" data-rawheight="366" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="486" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/a218d2340f0cc7ae848cb68aeae060ed_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="486" data-rawheight="366" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="486" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/a218d2340f0cc7ae848cb68aeae060ed_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/a218d2340f0cc7ae848cb68aeae060ed_b.jpg"><br><blockquote>那呆子闻得此言，战兢兢跑将转来，相近唐僧，且不回话，放下钯，<b>在那里出恭</b>。行者见了，喝道：“你不回话，却蹲在那里怎的？”</blockquote><br><blockquote>八戒道：“<b>唬出屎来了!</b>如今也不消说，赶早儿各自顾命去罢！”</blockquote>


</div>

</div>
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden ac" name="9138141-comment"></a>
