<div class="zm-item" id="mi-1379517091">
<h2 class="zm-item-title ">
<a href="/collection/26533463">自我完善</a>
</h2>
<div class="zm-item-meta">

<a href="/people/baobanxian" data-tip="p$t$baobanxian" class="zg-link-litblue"> 包半仙 </a> 创建


<span style="color: #dddddd;">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span>
<a class="zg-link-gray" href="/collection/26533463/followers">2 人关注</a>

